bilingual.source: Scott Kelly's identical twin brother, Mark, is also an astronaut.
bilingual.target: 斯科特·凯利的同卵双胞胎兄弟马克也是宇航员。

bilingual.source: The twin sisters share a special bond.
bilingual.target: 这对双胞胎姐妹有一种特殊的联系。

bilingual.source: She disguised herself as her twin sister.
bilingual.target: 她假扮成她的双胞胎妹妹。

bilingual.source: The audience cheered for his twin killing.
bilingual.target: 观众们为他的双杀欢呼雀跃。

bilingual.source: Her twin sister looks like her mirror image.
bilingual.target: 她的双胞胎姐妹看起来像她的镜像。

bilingual.source: My twin brother and I have the same birthday.
bilingual.target: 我的双胞胎兄弟和我有相同的生日。

bilingual.source: The twin babies were born just minutes apart.
bilingual.target: 这对双胞胎婴儿出生时间仅相隔几分钟。

bilingual.source: He built wooden cradles for his twin daughters.
bilingual.target: 他为双胞胎女儿制作了木制摇篮。

bilingual.source: This twin killing was a highlight of his career.
bilingual.target: 这次双杀是他职业生涯中的一个亮点。

yingyinNormal.en: What? My identical hand twin. What's an identical hand twin?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？我的双胞手啊！什么是双胞手？
汉斯？汉斯！邪恶的双胞胎。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what's not one of a kind? A twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么最不独一无二？双胞胎。

yingyinNormal.en: Except he's a boxer, and has an evil twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除了他是拳击手之外，还有一个坏蛋双胞胎兄弟。

yingyinNormal.en: Me? Oh come on, man. You can't do this. Come on. I'm your hand twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我？别这样嘛。走吧。你不能这样，我是你的双胞手耶。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Phoebe. Yeah. I found my identical hand twin. Oh, you're so lucky.
yingyinNormal.zh: 菲比，我找到我的双胞手了！你真幸运。

yingyinNormal.en: My dream is to hang a high wire between those Twin Towers, and walk on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的梦想就是在世贸双子星中间架起钢索，然后走过它。

yingyinNormal.en: Chandler. You are not gonna believe this. I have found my identical hand twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 钱德，说了你一定不相信，我找到我的双胞手了！

yingyinNormal.en: Or as everyone in the world calls them, the Twin Towers of the World Trade Center.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世人都称呼它们：世贸双子星。

yingyinNormal.en: Lucky your guy had a twin brother, and lucky that brother wasn't some oral hygienist or something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 幸好你那位科学家有个孪生弟弟，幸好他也不是什么口腔医生。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me? She's my twin sister. She thinks she's funny, but frankly, I've never been able to see it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 啊？她是我的孪生妹妹，她以为自己很风趣，但说实话，我从来看不出。

yingyinNormal.en: Why are you doing this? I got to know. What's your M.O. What gets you out of that twin bed in the morning?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么要做这个？我必须要问问，你的动力是什么？是什么激励你早上起床？

yingyinNormal.en: Zoe's baby twin sisters Zuzu and Zaza want to join the sleepover too. But the sleepover is only for big girls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佐伊的双胞胎妹妹们，祖祖和莎莎也想和她们过夜。过夜派对只能让大姑娘们参加，知道吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Zoe's baby twin sisters Zuzu and Zaza want to join the sleepover too. But the sleepover is only for big girls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佐伊的双胞胎妹妹们，祖祖和莎莎也想和她们过夜。过夜派对只能让大姑娘们参加，知道吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Zoe's baby twin sisters Zuzu and Zaza want to join the sleepover too. But the sleepover is only for big girls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佐伊的双胞胎妹妹也想加入她们一起过夜。但是与朋友过夜只是大一点的女孩专利。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, twin stuff is always a real big seller. What? Yeah, I can talk them into giving you like, 30 dollars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 双胞胎的题材一向很热卖。什么？我可以帮你谈到30块钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Drake, what are you getting at? I'm not Drake. That's right! He's not Drake. He's Hans Ramoray, Drake's evil twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 德瑞克，你到底要说什么？我不是德瑞克，没错，他不是德瑞克，他是汉斯雷莫瑞，德瑞克邪恶的双胞胎兄弟。

yingyinNormal.en: She was married to a gay ice dancer. She gave birth to her brother's triplets. Oh. Oh. Her twin sister used to do porn.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她曾跟男同志冰舞选手结婚，她帮她弟弟生下三胞胎，她的双胞胎姐姐是A片演员。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah but Pottery Barn. You know what I think? It's just she's weird. You know it's because she's a twin. Twins are weird.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是陶瓷货仓耶，我觉得根本是她太怪，因为她是双胞胎，双胞胎都很怪。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: To the horror of some who expected a Greek Revival <highlight>twin</highlight> of the Treasury Building to be erected, the elaborate French Second Empire style was selected.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 令那些期待着财政部大楼会像希腊复兴一样被建造起来的人们恐惧的是，一座精巧的法国第二帝国风格的建筑被选中了。
